IDEA: To preserve a body perfectly, a unique but complicated process can be done.
Upon the invention of Khueenite, Nul Detta took advantage of this and used its properties to modify the Fracturing and NulGraven.
When both properties are within close proximity (this included Fracturing Zones and NulGraven Sites), they naturally repell one another, with the repulsion rate and severity depending on Memetta and Dett Minor's opinions towards each other.
However, if someone was placed in between these two poles of force, and both forces are pulled away violently, the MEMORIES and SENTIENCE of the person is extracted at immense speeds and stored within those respective NulGraven and Fracturing forces. Without a proper soul, but with both Phatnasmal phenomena within close proximity, the soul-less body is then subjected to a process similar to Khueenite, where it petrifies and turns into stone. Upon returning the memories and sentience to this stone, the person within is brought back to life.
This same process is used on petrified Infinitus Caradels, explaining what those massive stone spikes around Spire islands are.